{"tid":2104092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者稱內地早知病毒人傳人　港大：報道與關鍵事實不符","createTime":"2020-07-11T16:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T02:25:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"680a7d232dc72b58c6281f62e161041c3c799a21","tid":2104092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537217-20200711.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537217-20200711.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=b7189208\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537217-20200711.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3d9c3cb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537217-20200711.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n曾經在香港大學參與病毒學研究的內地學者閻麗夢，在美國接受傳媒訪問，指年初發現新型冠狀病毒在武漢有人傳人，但內地當局沒有披露有關消息，她匯報予港大的上司潘烈文，對方叫她保持沉默，又指潘烈文警告過她，不要觸碰紅線。<br />\n<br />\n港大表示，有關報道的內容與關鍵事實不符，又指閻麗夢沒有在她提及的時期，參與病毒人傳人研究。"},{"pid":"ba9ce066eae4af362f47c95333395ec6fcbbe3e1","tid":2104092,"uid":79563,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"HKU個回應, 其實係好鬼：<br />\n<br />\n(1)  「有關報道的內容與關鍵事實不符」= 與關鍵事實不符, 即係「與部份事實是相符」，而呢方面相符既事實, 港大認為係「非關鍵」<br />\n<br />\n(2)  「閻麗夢沒有在她提及的時期，參與病毒人傳人研究。」 = 即係閻麗夢在其他時期，有參與病毒人傳人研究。"},{"pid":"8af3e6710f0213df2d4b494b5dbeefefecdc62ff","tid":2104092,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"咁有冇警告過佢先"},{"pid":"8bb312762f69df4a829d0984c24bc977bfa4540e","tid":2104092,"uid":143343,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76c82f0c2b2141ba79110fa1e87ce27f7d269103","tid":2104092,"uid":79563,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:27:21.000Z","msg":"簡單嚟講<br />\n<br /